OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FFamilies of the victims of the
OL,7,FBirmingham pub bombings are calling on
OL,8,Fthe government to launch a public
OL,9,Finquiry into the atrocity, as ITV
OL,10,FNews' Ben Chapman reports
OL,12,FRelatives of people killed in the
OL,13,FBirmingham pub bombings have called
OL,14,Ffor a public inquiry on the 50th
OL,15,Fanniversary of the biggest unsolved
OL,16,Fmass murder in modern British history.
OL,18,FTwenty-one people were killed and more
OL,19,Fthan 200 injured when two bombs
OL,20,Fexploded minutes apart in two city-
OL,21,Fcentre pubs in November 1974.
