OL,6,FThe IRA is thought to have been
OL,7,Fresponsible, despite never claiming
OL,8,Fresponsibility.
OL,10,FSix men, who became known as the
OL,11,F'Birmingham Six,' were wrongly
OL,12,Fconvicted of murder but cleared in
OL,13,F1991.
OL,15,FNo one has since been charged in
OL,16,Fconnection with the attacks.
OL,18,FFor the families of those killed, the
OL,19,Fabsence of justice has only compounded
OL,20,Fdecades of pain.
