OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,F"It's not gone away," says Pauline
OL,7,FCurzon, whose 19-year-old sister,
OL,8,FPamela Palmer, was killed while
OL,9,Fenjoying an evening out with her
OL,10,Fboyfriend.
OL,12,F"She'd sat down near the jukebox,
OL,13,Fwhich is where they think the bomb had
OL,14,Fbeen placed," Pauline said.
OL,16,F"The fact that it's unsolved, it
OL,17,Fdoesn't give you any peace of mind. I
OL,18,Ffeel a bit cynical. I think they know.
OL,19,FBut they're not going to tell us."
