OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FBy 'they,' Pauline means the British
OL,7,Fstate, which she and many of the other
OL,8,Ffamilies suspect of withholding
OL,9,Finformation about the bombings for
OL,10,Fdecades, including about whether it
OL,11,Fcould have been prevented.
OL,13,FAfter years of campaigning, they
OL,14,Fsecured inquests into the 21 deaths in
OL,15,F2019, only to be disappointed by what
OL,16,Fthey saw as the limited scope of the
OL,17,Fhearings.
