OL,6,FIn recent years, the names of
OL,7,Fpotential suspects have begun to
OL,8,Femerge.
OL,10,FAt the inquests in 2019, a convicted
OL,11,FIRA bomber known as "Witness O" named
OL,12,Ffour of the men responsible as Seamus
OL,13,FMcLoughlin, Mick Murray, James Gavin
OL,14,Fand Michael Hayes.
OL,16,FOf those, only Michael Hayes is still
OL,17,Falive. Following the inquests, he told
OL,18,FITV News: "I didn't do it."
