OL,6,FIn 2018, an ITV Exposure documentary
OL,7,Fidentified a man living in Belfast,
OL,8,FMichael Patrick Reilly, as a potential
OL,9,Fsuspect. He strongly denies any
OL,10,Finvolvement in the bombings.
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police are reported to
OL,13,Fhave arrested and questioned him in
OL,14,F2020 but he was released without
OL,15,Fcharge.
OL,17,FThe Crown Prosecution Service
OL,18,Fconfirmed last year there had been
OL,19,F"insufficient evidence" to bring any
OL,20,Fnew charges.
